#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_reasoning_and_discovery.ipynb:110010
#: 7af4c8d3058743ad8dbd15a5aec1b3c6
msgid ""
"A **Causal DAG** represents a single, fully oriented data-generating "
"structure where every edge has a direction (e.g., `media_activities → "
"brand_search → purchase`). It encodes a complete causal story."
msgstr ""
"msgid: A **Causal DAG** represents a single, fully oriented data-generating structure where every edge has a direction (e.g., `media_activities → brand_search → purchase`). It encodes a complete causal story.  \n"
"msgstr: Un **DAG Causal** representa una única estructura generadora de datos completamente orientada donde cada arista tiene una dirección (por ejemplo, `media_activities → brand_search → purchase`). Codifica una historia causal completa."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_reasoning_and_discovery.ipynb:110012
#: 199d2732571c46389af3bdc67fa088cc
msgid ""
"A **CPDAG**, on the other hand, represents a **Markov equivalence class**: "
